{"tid":2051733,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"捷克眾議院拒絕感謝台灣提供的專用防護裝備","createTime":"2020-06-05T03:55:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T06:56:03.000Z","uid":39876,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"82d0aefbd08fa919861e37175275349df0946b03","tid":2051733,"uid":39876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:55:12.000Z","msg":"4月份，台灣免費向捷克共和國送去了80萬口罩，25台呼吸機和100套醫用防護。當時，反對派和參議院代表公開感謝他們的交付。<br />\n<br />\n在特別會議上，<span style=\"color: red;\">眾議院拒絕感謝台灣為該國在對抗冠狀病毒方面提供的免費援助。該提案未得到執政聯盟，捷克和摩拉維亞共產黨（KSČM)和自由與直接民主黨（SPD)成員的支持。<br />\n</span><br />\n議長馮德拉西克說，他個人感謝台灣官員的幫助。他解釋說：&ldquo;我們也不必為所有事情投票，有些事情是顯而易見的。&rdquo; 外交部長托馬斯&middot;佩特里奇克（CSSD）說，感謝所有提供援助的國家。揚&middot;巴托舍克（KDU-ČSL）說：&ldquo;我感謝政府感謝她，但我們要感謝你作為眾議院的代表。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nODS議會俱樂部主席ZbyněkStanjura開始批評眾議院議長：&ldquo;您喜歡在收到禮物後拍照。您拍攝了照片，並稱讚自己收到了台灣的禮物，但是為了支持一個體面的人類請求感謝您的免費幫助，您棄權英勇。<br />\n<br />\n瑪麗安&middot;尤雷奇卡（KDU-ČSL）也批評了這一舉動：&ldquo;一個已經到來的國家免費為一些城市和機構提供了援助，我們只應該禮貌地感謝它。眾議院將沒有多數會說，親愛的政府，謝謝您的幫助。我不明白這個。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n午休之前，歐洲議會議員根本沒有時間投票感謝台灣。CSSD代表Jan Chvojka反對將會議時間推遲到下午1點的代表，這一點直到下午2.30才被投票。也就是說，在議會小組有足夠的時間休息之後，可以就相互協調進行磋商。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">政黨ANO和CSSD以及KSCM有足夠的時間來尋找更多的支持者，以防止休會後達成一項可能損害與中華人民共和國關係的決議。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.novinky.cz/domaci/clanek/poslanci-odmitli-podekovat-tchaj-wanu-40326571\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.novinky.cz%2Fdomaci%2Fclanek%2Fposlanci-odmitli-podekovat-tchaj-wanu-40326571&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5EjYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=db3c472f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.novinky.cz/domaci/clanek/poslanci-odmitli-podekovat-tchaj-wanu-40326571</a>"},{"pid":"811313d5adfc9ac32554c2ffa22863fb44d66e6b","tid":2051733,"uid":39876,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歐盟"},{"pid":"a6f0735c7feff7ff1c5597f40c4c02b4297fe6b3","tid":2051733,"uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:58:48.000Z","msg":"邊個唔撚感謝咪唔撚好用囉，冇人逼你用"},{"pid":"629577190abfa02d9efb0f35ac49193ae605c09f","tid":2051733,"uid":4942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T04:00:30.000Z","msg":"捷克仲要奶番共產黨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9fcd10c10f24b8d9cc7b2ae7bfd3c2794074eb8","tid":2051733,"uid":241567,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T04:01:15.000Z","msg":"而家用黎試鬼一流 <br />\n係人係鬼清楚哂"},{"pid":"b3515b688fb026f78913551af7d6573fc7846a54","tid":2051733,"uid":200049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T04:02:20.000Z","msg":"捷克咁垃圾 狗也不屌"},{"pid":"80956359ea087a26f9e0626c1e7e1ae1cf20cf85","tid":2051733,"uid":15010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T04:03:34.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾EU"},{"pid":"d0107746cf5da293d6bf3d66215ffc6f18d7ec09","tid":2051733,"uid":223664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T04:04:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />果然成個歐洲都一舊舊"},{"pid":"616542f41731e2338d7a8e8b83cd903fa212aff5","tid":2051733,"uid":207247,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T04:05:22.000Z","msg":"班垃圾咪撚用台灣裝備囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵支那幫手啦，d 口罩唔合格比人退貨"},{"pid":"6286bba3d5036ab2daf84857639288e614a6962b","tid":2051733,"uid":183844,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T04:07:38.000Z","msg":"人都不如<br />\n應該投票點樣多謝台灣<br />\n而不是應否多謝台灣<br />\n作為政府不用報恩 僅僅謝恩都做唔到<br />\n垃圾"},{"pid":"aa8f1f20464ee62003544af413c06ed64b28aa5c","tid":2051733,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05